’Щ@ec07ea8349f649f3ce6be251ed7e849704c2340481d5a078cffee42e1b7f4ef0ЪTitle: title: load-env
Path: Examples
Content:
Load variables from an input stream.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> {NAME: ABE, AGE: UNKNOWN} | load-env; $env.NAME
ABE

```
Load variables from an argument.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> load-env {NAME: ABE, AGE: UNKNOWN}; $env.NAME
ABE

```
